prompts.frontCover: A charming watercolor painting of a cartoon sloth wearing a tiny, crooked party hat, hanging upside-down from a lush green branch. The sloth has a comically slow and blissful smile, holding a single, half-melted birthday candle with a tiny wisp of smoke. Below the branch, the words "happy belated-ish birthday" are elegantly scripted in a beautiful, readable handwritten cursive. The artwork is flat 2D, with soft, flowing watercolor textures, artistic brush strokes, and organic paint bleeds on a textured paper background. The overall style is humorous, lighthearted, and endearing.
